@startuml
title StayFinder - System Context
left to right direction

actor "Người dùng cuối" as User
rectangle "StayFinder Mobile App" as App
rectangle "StayFinder API Server" as API
database "Supabase Postgres" as DB
rectangle "RAG Pipeline" as RAG
rectangle "Crawler + Normalizer" as Crawl

User --> App : Tìm kiếm, xem chi tiết,\nchat AI
App --> API : REST/JSON
API --> DB : SQL queries
API --> RAG : Query/Generate\nReview Summary
RAG --> DB : Read chunks,\nwrite cache summaries
Crawl --> DB : Import compact dataset

@enduml
